data.description: Excellent opportunity to renovate and build the home of your dreams. Situated on a quiet residential street of Bayonne on a 25x133 lot. This cozy Colonial home has so much potential. First floor features enclosed porch, living room with fireplace, formal dining room, eat in kitchen. Second floor features 3  bedrooms and 1 full bath. Shared driveway with 2 car garage and backyard. 203K or cash offers only. Services are off, sale completely as-is, where is. Buyer responsible for CCO. Bring your vision and tools!
